---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy – Stop Suing Valve" description="Privacy policy for Stop Suing Valve. We do not track you beyond strictly necessary means and do not sell your data.">
	<article class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
		<header class="mb-12 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-4 dark:text-stone-100">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-stone-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto dark:text-stone-400">
				We respect your privacy. This policy explains what we do and do not do with your data when you use this website.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-stone-600 space-y-6 text-left dark:text-stone-400">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">What we collect</h2>
				<p>
					We do not run analytics trackers or advertising on this site. We collect personal data only in the following ways:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li><strong>Newsletter subscription:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address, optionally your name, and your subscription preferences (which update lists you want to receive).</li>
					<li><strong>Email contact:</strong> If you email us at contact@stopsuingvalve.com, we collect your message and contact details.</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">
					We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Newsletter and email communications</h2>
				<p>
					Our newsletter is managed using <strong>Listmonk</strong>, a self-hosted open-source mailing list manager. Emails are sent via <strong>SMTP2GO</strong>, a third-party email delivery service. When you subscribe:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li>Your email address and name (if provided) are stored on our self-hosted Listmonk server.</li>
					<li>Your email address is transmitted to SMTP2GO solely for the purpose of delivering emails to you.</li>
					<li>We use ALTCHA, a privacy-friendly CAPTCHA, to prevent spam subscriptions. ALTCHA does not use cookies or track you.</li>
					<li>You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email, or by contacting us.</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">
					We will only send you emails related to the topics you subscribed to (e.g., lawsuit updates, consumer news, developer news).
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Cookies</h2>
				<p>
					We use only strictly necessary means to run the site:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li><strong>Cookie banner acknowledgment:</strong> We store a simple flag in your browser's localStorage to remember that you have acknowledged the cookie banner. This is not a cookie and contains no personal data.</li>
					<li><strong>ALTCHA verification:</strong> The CAPTCHA widget does not set cookies or store personal data.</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">
					We do not use cookies for advertising, tracking, or analytics.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Third-party services</h2>
				<p>
					We use the following third-party services:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our site is hosted and protected by Cloudflare. Cloudflare may collect standard server logs (IP address, browser, requested URL) for security and operation. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-stone-300">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
					<li><strong>SMTP2GO:</strong> Used to deliver newsletter emails. See <a href="https://www.smtp2go.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-stone-300">SMTP2GO's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Data retention</h2>
				<p>
					Newsletter subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion. Email correspondence is retained as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and for our records, unless you request deletion.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Your rights</h2>
				<p>
					You have the right to:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
					<li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
					<li>Request deletion of your data</li>
					<li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
					<li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">
					To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@stopsuingvalve.com" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-stone-300">contact@stopsuingvalve.com</a>. We will respond within 30 days.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2 dark:text-stone-100">Changes</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The current version will always be on this page. Last updated: January 2026.
				</p>
			</section>

			<p class="text-sm text-stone-500 pt-4 text-center dark:text-stone-500">
				Contact: <a href="mailto:contact@stopsuingvalve.com" class="text-stone-700 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-stone-300">contact@stopsuingvalve.com</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>
